    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a system to house Ukrainian families with children in the UK",
        "additional_details": "Being a veteran of our British Army and the space and willingness I will do whatever I need to do to provide safety for children who are now in conflict within Europe. I think this is the least we can do to help the innocent Ukrainian people.",
        "background": "Put into place a simple system in which Ukrainian families with children can apply to enter the United Kingdom via a neighbouring nation such as Poland and be sponsored to stay at a DBS-checked family home within our country during this immediate disgraceful act of aggression.",
